Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.54,0:02:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真梦 那个岛田真梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 现在好像在仙台的叫「Wake Up. Girls!」里活动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然传言都是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下个专题 这就决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去采访真梦么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 签名应该都像这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:02:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对没有那种的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放晴娘？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是咧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝里 真梦梦怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听说 不知道怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会迟到还真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个工作定下来了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家准备好狂喜乱舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.09,0:03:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继电视之后 这次又是广播的常规出演
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅是常规的连续节目 还有冠名哦~
