Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要取回曾经失去的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.14,0:21:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想必会比最初更困难
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我更加坚定了决心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.64,0:21:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应援再次挑战梦想的岛田真梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志保？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//NEXT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.91,0:23:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真梦梦真是一个充满谜团的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.47,0:23:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝蓝你是她的好朋友应该知道不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.91,0:23:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道 不过那个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.71,0:23:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.44,0:23:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她身上痣的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.60,0:23:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疯狂…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:23:59.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一集 「是天国还是地狱？」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//NEXT-END
